#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:86
msgid "Adding a serialization format"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:88
msgid ""
"A serialization format controls how the ``TUSummary`` is written to (and "
"read from) disk. This involves more boilerplate than an extractor because "
"each format has a per-analysis ``FormatInfo`` sub-registry."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:92
msgid "Step 1: Define the format class"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:94
msgid ""
