"``FormatInfo`` type alias:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:118
msgid "Step 2: Register the format"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:138
msgid ""
"The format name (``\"myformat\"``) is matched against the file extension in "
"``--ssaf-tu-summary-file=output.myformat``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:141
msgid "Step 3: Register per-analysis FormatInfo entries"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:143
msgid ""
"For each analysis that should be serializable in your format, register a "
"``FormatInfo`` entry. ``FormatInfo`` must be implemented for any of the "
"summaries that wants to support ``myformat``:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:164
msgid "Step 4: Add the force-linker anchor"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/developer-docs/HowToExtend.rst:166
msgid ""
"Same pattern as for extractors — add the anchor to ``BuiltinAnchorSources."
"def`` (in alphabetical order). See `Adding a summary extractor`_ Step 3, "
"and :doc:`ForceLinkerHeaders`."
msgstr ""

